import React, { useState } from "react"; import TopNav from "../components/TopNav"; import { Container, Row, Col, Card, Form, Button } from "react-bootstrap"; import { predictSingle } from "../services/api"; import { toast } from "react-toastify"; export default function PredictSingle() { const [form, setForm] = useState({ name: "Test Student", district: "Chennai", passed_out_10: 2022, passed_out_11: 2023, passed_out_12: 2024, marks_10: 80, marks_11: 85, marks_12: 88, family_income: 20000, family_members: 4, academic_score: 75, motivation_level: 3, attendance_rate: 80, school_type_10: "Government", school_type_11: "Government", school_type_12: "Government", orphan: "No", single_parent: "No", girl_child: "No", communication_frequency: "Medium", family_support: "Medium", extra_curricular: "No", interest_level: "Medium", attitude: "Respectful", school_fee_6_to_12: "10k-20k", }); const [result, setResult] = useState(null); const update = (key, value) => { setForm((prev) => ({ ...prev, [key]: value })); }; const submit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); try { const res = await predictSingle(form); setResult(res); toast.success("Prediction success"); } catch (err) { toast.error("Prediction failed"); } }; return ( <>
{/* ------------------- ACADEMIC ------------------- */}
Academic Information
Academic Score update("academic_score", +e.target.value)} /> Motivation Level (1â€“5) update("motivation_level", +e.target.value)} /> Attendance Rate (%) update("attendance_rate", +e.target.value)} /> Marks 10 update("marks_10", +e.target.value)} /> Marks 11 update("marks_11", +e.target.value)} /> Marks 12 update("marks_12", +e.target.value)} /> {/* ------------------- FAMILY ------------------- */}
Family Information
Family Income update("family_income", +e.target.value)} /> Family Members update("family_members", +e.target.value)} /> Orphan update("orphan", e.target.value)} > Single Parent update("single_parent", e.target.value)} > Girl Child update("girl_child", e.target.value)} > {/* ------------------- SCHOOL / SUPPORT ------------------- */}
School Information
{["school_type_10", "school_type_11", "school_type_12"].map( (k) => ( {k.replace(/_/g, " ").toUpperCase()} update(k, e.target.value)} > ) )}
Behaviour & Support
Family Support update("family_support", e.target.value)} > Communication Frequency update("communication_frequency", e.target.value) } > Interest Level update("interest_level", e.target.value)} >
{/* ------------------- RESULT ------------------- */}
Prediction Result
{result ? ( <>

Dropout Probability: {result.dropout_probability}
